snippet.title: ANXRacers Trailer Pre-Final Trailer 2*
snippet.description:
*Music is not Final
ANXRacers is a 2D top-down time-attack spaceship racing game. 
As a racing pilot, your goal is to get the spaceship from start to finish, in the least amount of time, while passing checkpoints in correct order. 

Get the game at https://studios.aeonax.com/racers/ or https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.aeonax.racers
